description: UkeChords give webOS users access to Ukulele Chords, presented in tablature form, for easy reference while on the go. The app currently includes charts for major, minor and 7th chords.
versionNote: Version 1.1.1 corrects an issue where 7th 'dominant' chords were incorrectly labelled 7th 'major' chords. Thanks to Joseph T for pointing this out!
